                      <p>
                          Here's how to reset your password:
                      <ol>
                          <li>
                              Open Lockdown on iPhone or iPad
                          </li>
                          <li>
                              Tap Account on bottom right
                          </li>
                          <li>
                              Sign Out
                          </li>
                          <li>
                              Tap Account on bottom right
                          </li>
                          <li>
                              Sign In
                          </li>
                          <li>
                              Forgot Password
                          </li>
                          <li>
