                      If I subscribe to the Secure Tunnel, can I share this with my family?
                  </a>
                  <div id="account5" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="family-share" data-parent="#account">
                      <hr />
                      <p>
                          <strong>Yes!</strong> To share the subscription with your family's devices, do the following:
                          <br />
                      <ol>
                          <li>
                              On your own device, subscribe to Secure Tunnel.
                          </li>
                          <li>
                              On that same device, make sure you're logged into Lockdown with your email, by tapping the "Account" tab
