              <div class="card-header border-0 my-2" id="uninstall">
                  <a href="#" class="btn btn-header-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#support2"
                     aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="support1">
                      How do I uninstall Lockdown Mac?
                  </a>
                  <div id="support2" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="uninstall" data-parent="#support2">
                      <hr />
                      <p>
                          Here's how to completely uninstall Lockdown on your Mac.
                      <ol>
                          <li>
                              Click the Lockdown button in the top right menu bar on your Mac to open the popup (it's a picture of a
                              lock)
                          </li>
                          <li>
                              Click the menu (three stripes) button
                          </li>
                          <li>
                              Click Quit. It will ask if you want to deactivate. Click yes.
                          </li>
                          <li>
                              Click your Wifi icon in the menu bar
                          </li>
                          <li>
                              Click "Network Preferences"
                          </li>
                          <li>
                              On the left, select "Lockdown Configuration", then click the "-" minus icon (on the bottom left of this dialog box)
                          </li>
                          <li>
                              On the left again, select "Lockdown VPN", then click the "-" minus icon again
                          </li>
                          <li>
                              Click "Apply"
